snippet.textDisplay: Brings back memories of when I was three in Christmas of '93.  Back then, all I played was my older sister's NES, but when I was given a huge box with my first console inside with loads of accessories, I screamed with joy.  This was the first game I played while my dad kept pestering me to shut it off and watch him play with the Super Scope.  The SNES was and always will be MY first gaming console.
